{"tid":392814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個憨鳩既中學同學","createTime":"2017-09-08T17:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T18:17:00.000Z","uid":75457,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56ec77ac4806123352816173bc907edec630b698","tid":392814,"uid":75457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:48:02.000Z","msg":"中學有一年嘅旅行日去郊野公園到燒嘢食同打邊爐，咁老師叫我哋圍內分幾組，分咗組之後我哋就分配邊個帶咩嘢食，其中叫咗個中學同學準備個爐，準備聽日打邊爐用，點不知旅行嗰日，佢淨係帶咗個爐冇帶gas同埋個煲，之後佢仲話你淨係叫我帶爐冇叫我帶其他嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最尾仲要我哋出錢去買返個煲同gas，臨尾食完仲要我哋去洗完之後個煲仲要送俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29bf0ea78437bc3b7cf9e1805e82049ae3c4607","tid":392814,"uid":128993,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:49:37.000Z","msg":"樓主意思係咪你同你班朋友係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e49316364ef3910762aba9a6a7ca77fa8190509","tid":392814,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:54:46.000Z","msg":"F3参加保良局啲19camp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一晚兩班男人同一間房玩到吵到拆天<br />\n第二日比人罰<br />\n<br />\n第二日有個戇鳩仔玩個活動好驚大叫 好撚驚呀快撚啲放我落嚟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後比人單獨捉出去鬧，比人聽到佢報串話我哋個晚係到講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後尾個呀sir睬佢都廢事冇理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec9166d52233d3a46885514fa560b6adf9c3856","tid":392814,"uid":75457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T18:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>F3参加保良局啲19camp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一晚兩班男人同一間房玩到吵到拆天<br />\n第二日比人罰<br />\n<br />\n第二日有個戇鳩仔玩個活動好驚大叫 好撚驚呀快撚啲放我落嚟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後比人單獨捉出去鬧，比人聽到佢報串話我哋個晚係到講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後尾個呀sir睬佢都廢事冇理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前中學都試過有班人係到打緊交，有條友出去報串，個啊sir黎到，班睇水既即刻叫班人走，啊sir黎到乜人都捉唔到就返番教員室，之後報串個條友比人係廁所打到流哂鼻血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5840a7917994734cc41a2bbe0d96b986262d2896","tid":392814,"uid":110734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T18:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主意思係咪你同你班朋友係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"53a8f28f8cca748e9176411bb8f8ba86477dcd68","tid":392814,"uid":110734,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T18:08:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主意思係咪你同你班朋友係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主複述個條友嘅回應係 &ldquo;帶個爐&rdquo;，但描述件事就用&ldquo;準備個爐&rdquo;，後者比較唔自然。可見樓主同佢朋友，當時未有向個條友提及gas爐其他配件。而重量及體積以人數分配來看，一人帶齊整套爐具亦不合理。<br />\n<br />\n結論：樓主on9"},{"pid":"0508e47e7577ea6a242da8add3b387aff684ed85","tid":392814,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T18:17:00.000Z","msg":"戇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}